<paragraph blockId="12.[213,1169,1037,1158]" pageId="12" pageNumber="937">
An adult female was collected. Shell length, 
<quantity box="[777,868,1038,1062]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.5" metricValueMax="4.0" metricValueMin="3.0" pageId="12" pageNumber="937" unit="mm" value="3.5" valueMax="4.0" valueMin="3.0">3–4 mm</quantity>
, thin, translucent, white, equivalve, semi-elliptical, with straight hinge line. Shell external sculpture a fine reticulate network of riblets and concentric striae. Shell valves widely splayed to mimic a limpet-like mode of life.
</paragraph>
